channel.title: Could ANY one recommend a New Source I could use
channel.description:
After my old source failed me (I have no Idea why :| it works for everyone else - [glow=red,2,300]Testscape[/glow]) I need a new one, but have no idea which sources are any good.
I am really looking for one with [u]all[/u] fully working skills and just a few NPC's So i can mould it into my own creation.
[glow=red,2,300]So which would you recommend[/glow]
If you've read this please reply...[br][size=1]Posted at: October 27, 2006, 05:52:55 AM[/size][hr]So no-one Knows any decent Sources... ________________________________________________________________________________

item.title: Could ANY one recommend a New Source I could use
item.dc:creator: @HelpmePl0x HelpmePl0x
item.description:
@HelpmePl0x wrote:

Problem was I could only hold about 6 people before an error message came up, then after that no-one else could log on, Ill post the error message now.[br][size=1]Posted at: October 27, 2006, 08:59:40 AM[/size][hr]Exception in thread “Thread-0” java.lang.OutofMemoryError: Java heap space.

I wasn’t sure what was up with it, But after talking to Mod Taharok he said that it was to do with my Compile.bat. After fixing that He eventually said I should change my Source, hence the reasoning for this Topic.

Do you guys have any idea what is up with it?[br][size=1]Posted at: October 27, 2006, 09:03:53 AM[/size][hr]May have fixed it not 100% certain.

Why did testscape fail you? did you get the 100 errors while adding something?
